# Lecture 10: UI Components / jQuery
---

Welcome to Lecture 10! Here's a brief rundown.

![bricks](https://media3.giphy.com/media/OMeGDxdAsMPzW/giphy.gif)

#### Learning Objectives

Get comfortable with UI component creation, jQuery

#### Rundown
Here's the game plan for today, fam.

#### [Review HW](http://samantha.fewd.us/#broadcast/mottaquikarim/FEWD629_functions_pset_2)
